      "date": "2016-04-27 21:30:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTotally in favour of the getstatus->get_root change.  Based on the number of changes, I'd think that subtree->fileset would have been the less invasive change, and leaves the possibility of non-subtree filesets open for the future, though I don't have a strong opinion.\n\nThe only other minor concern is that some patches in flight are checking for a non-zero \"$FILESET\" to skip tests related to fid2path or similar.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
